# fintech_case1
first case study
Who are you? Daniel Singer What is your background? Finance degree, working in commodity trading
What are your career goals? Build a fintech/defi enabled supply chain management tool to optimize the supply chain & make SCF collateral based where lending or investing rules are related to market based inventory valuation
Why did you choose Fintech as a career path? I believe agricultural commodity trade has structural problems which fintech and supply chain technologies can jointly solve